      "detailed_description": "<h1>Just Updated</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/444200/extras/wotb_ka_004_upd_11.8_stm_920x430_ww.png?t=1747909796\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">— Operation Interference and a Legendary camo for the AMX 50 100.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">— Exciting activities throughout April and May that will bring you a heap of rewards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">— Fun modes: 10v10, Realistic Battles, Mad Games, Big Boss, and Uprising.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">— New Legendary camos for the IS-8, K-91, and Controcarro 1 Mk. 2 to make a glitzy impression in battle!</p></p><br><h1>Update Notes</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fantasy and realistic camos, activities to suit all tastes, and stunning prizes. Jump into Blitz and win big!</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It's World of Tanks Blitz, a legendary action-adventure tank game. Blitz is not about war, but tanks! Join this action-packed PvP shooter and explore unique vehicles and a variety of battlefields. Experience the adrenaline rush of intense tank battles that test your skills and strategy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This FREE tank game keeps you engaged and brings everyday challenges and unique events. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/444200/extras/Banners__616px_.png?t=1747909796\" /><br> </p>",
      "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It's World of Tanks Blitz, a legendary action-adventure tank game. Blitz is not about war, but tanks! Join this action-packed PvP shooter and explore unique vehicles and a variety of battlefields. Experience the adrenaline rush of intense tank battles that test your skills and strategy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This FREE tank game keeps you engaged and brings everyday challenges and unique events. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/444200/extras/Banners__616px_.png?t=1747909796\" /><br> </p>",
      "short_description": "Tanks, not war: jump into a free-to-play MMO action shooter with over 400 tanks. Enjoy stunning graphics and intuitive touch controls. Engage in 7vs7 battles, strategize with your team to conquer diverse maps. Customize tanks, unlock upgrades, and dive into adrenaline-pumping action on mobile and PC",
